What does a two-year-old eat?

881
00:39:40,537 --> 00:39:42,239
- Rice?
- He said milk.

882
00:39:42,305 --> 00:39:43,740
- Baby food?
- Milk.

883
00:39:43,807 --> 00:39:44,808
Milk!

884
00:39:45,642 --> 00:39:47,444
But there's formula.

885
00:39:48,645 --> 00:39:51,248
Should we give the baby formula milk?

886
00:39:51,314 --> 00:39:54,618
Mom told me to feed him
at around 11:30 a.m.

887
00:39:54,684 --> 00:39:56,386
- At 11:30 a.m.?
- It's late.

888
00:39:56,453 --> 00:39:57,954
He might be hungry.

889
00:39:58,021 --> 00:39:59,990
I just put one scoop
in this bottle, right?

890
00:40:00,056 --> 00:40:01,324
- Not two scoops.
- Right.

891
00:40:01,391 --> 00:40:02,859
HE CHECKS THE MEASUREMENTS
AND RUSHES TO THE KITCHEN

892
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:05,795
He's going to make you food.

893
00:40:05,862 --> 00:40:07,097
He'll make your milk.

894
00:40:07,163 --> 00:40:08,398
Milk.

895
00:40:10,367 --> 00:40:11,368
CHEF KWAK MAKES BABY FORMULA NOW

896
00:40:11,434 --> 00:40:12,702
I'll try making it.

897
00:40:14,971 --> 00:40:17,340
HYGIENE

898
00:40:17,407 --> 00:40:20,010
CLEANLINESS

899
00:40:22,345 --> 00:40:26,983
HE POURS FORMULA POWDER
INTO A MEASURING CUP FIRST

900
00:40:27,584 --> 00:40:30,020
CAREFUL

901
00:40:30,086 --> 00:40:31,254
STOPPING

902
00:40:31,321 --> 00:40:32,656
This isn't it.

903
00:40:33,723 --> 00:40:35,926
No, I should do it by hand.

904
00:40:35,992 --> 00:40:37,093
I'm nervous.

905
00:40:37,794 --> 00:40:38,795
The amount...

906
00:40:39,729 --> 00:40:41,564
ONE SCOOP

907
00:40:41,631 --> 00:40:43,566
ANOTHER SCOOP

908
00:40:43,967 --> 00:40:46,269
HE'S NEVER MADE FORMULA MILK BEFORE

909
00:40:46,836 --> 00:40:49,739
POURING EVERY LAST BIT

910
00:40:51,107 --> 00:40:53,944
HE CHECKS
IF THE LID IS CLOSED PROPERLY

911
00:40:54,010 --> 00:40:55,712
SHAKING

912
00:40:56,212 --> 00:41:00,016
OVERLY INTENSE FORMULA SHAKING

913
00:41:00,550 --> 00:41:04,054
THE BOTTLE SNAP IS
A FULL FOREARM WORKOUT

914
00:41:07,857 --> 00:41:09,359
It's Seon-hui and Da-in.

915
00:41:09,793 --> 00:41:11,361
- Are they here?
- Seriously?

916
00:41:11,428 --> 00:41:13,596
THE PART-TIMER JUMPS UP
AT THE ARRIVAL OF VIP REGULARS

917
00:41:15,498 --> 00:41:17,934
- Da-in and Seon-hui!
- Hi!

918
00:41:18,001 --> 00:41:19,736
- Uncle.
- Hi.

919
00:41:19,803 --> 00:41:21,771
We have a new, pretty staff member.

920
00:41:21,838 --> 00:41:22,973
"Pretty"?

921
00:41:23,039 --> 00:41:24,541
- Come say hi.
- "Pretty"?

922
00:41:24,607 --> 00:41:27,110
- Hi!
- Hello.

923
00:41:27,811 --> 00:41:29,813
- Hello.
- Hello.

924
00:41:30,013 --> 00:41:31,781
MEETING THE PRETTY PART-TIMER
FOR THE FIRST TIME

925
00:41:32,315 --> 00:41:34,818
- Hi.
- Hi.

926
00:41:35,352 --> 00:41:36,653
THE BABY BEAMS WITH A BIG SMILE

927
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,921
- Oh, he's so glad to see you.
- Hi!

928
00:41:37,988 --> 00:41:39,689
- Hi.
- Hi, Seo-yul.

929
00:41:39,756 --> 00:41:41,558
Who are you?

930
00:41:41,624 --> 00:41:43,560
I'm new here.

931
00:41:43,626 --> 00:41:47,597
- Are you a one-day part-timer?
- Yes, I'm here just for the day.

932
00:41:47,664 --> 00:41:49,532
What kind of work will you be doing?

933
00:41:50,367 --> 00:41:51,501
What do you think

934
00:41:51,968 --> 00:41:53,236
I should do here?

935
00:41:53,603 --> 00:41:54,871
Just enjoy it.

936
00:41:54,938 --> 00:41:56,139
- Enjoy it?
- Yes.

937
00:41:56,206 --> 00:41:58,141
I can feel the relaxed vibe

938
00:41:58,208 --> 00:41:59,943
of a regular.

939
00:42:00,276 --> 00:42:01,945
Is this for me?

940
00:42:02,012 --> 00:42:03,580
THE BARBERSHOP GETS
EVEN BUSIER WITH KIDS

941
00:42:03,646 --> 00:42:05,715
Your formula order is ready.

942
00:42:07,283 --> 00:42:09,452
- Sir, your formula is here.
- Sir.

943
00:42:09,519 --> 00:42:11,154
Oh, my, he feels good.

944
00:42:11,221 --> 00:42:12,455
SQUEALING MEANS HE'S HAPPY

945
00:42:12,856 --> 00:42:14,758
It's the perfect temperature
for drinking

946
00:42:15,658 --> 00:42:16,826
which is 23 degrees Celsius.

947
00:42:17,427 --> 00:42:19,462
It's rich in carbohydrates

948
00:42:19,529 --> 00:42:21,965
and packed
with vitamins and minerals, sir.

949
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:25,201
Do you like it, sir?

950
00:42:25,268 --> 00:42:26,936
- He likes it.
- Thank you.

951
00:42:27,637 --> 00:42:29,305
That formula must be very tasty.

952
00:42:29,906 --> 00:42:30,974
You like it?

953
00:42:31,041 --> 00:42:32,242
THE CUSTOMER IS SATISFIED

954
00:42:32,308 --> 00:42:35,111
The service here is amazing.

955
00:42:35,545 --> 00:42:36,846
Look at him.

956
00:42:37,747 --> 00:42:39,716
Is he getting drunk on formula?

957
00:42:40,083 --> 00:42:41,785
Oh, my. He's overdrinking.

958
00:42:41,851 --> 00:42:42,852
GULPING DOWN

959
00:42:44,454 --> 00:42:45,655
DROPS

960
00:42:45,722 --> 00:42:46,923
A vacation. No!

961
00:42:46,990 --> 00:42:48,224
- Are you okay?
- It's too...

962
00:42:48,291 --> 00:42:50,527
- I'll pick it up.
- It's okay.

963
00:42:50,827 --> 00:42:53,596
- I'll clean it and give it back.
- Clean it. Hygiene first.

964
00:42:54,164 --> 00:42:57,400
HE QUICKLY STERILIZES IT

965
