966
00:42:59,869 --> 00:43:01,337
MY FORMULA!

967
00:43:01,404 --> 00:43:02,806
WHINING

968
00:43:02,872 --> 00:43:04,674
Here's your milk.

969
00:43:04,741 --> 00:43:06,709
YUM

970
00:43:07,877 --> 00:43:10,180
PEACE RESTORED, BACK TO DRINKING

971
00:43:10,847 --> 00:43:13,116
- There's a painting.
- Oh, no.

972
00:43:13,183 --> 00:43:15,952
- The formula...
- Uncle, wash it again!

973
00:43:16,686 --> 00:43:19,289
2ND STERILIZATION

974
00:43:20,190 --> 00:43:22,959
Your formula is coming.

975
00:43:23,226 --> 00:43:24,627
RUSHING

976
00:43:25,161 --> 00:43:26,262
Here it is.

977
00:43:26,329 --> 00:43:27,730
The big girls brought it.

978
00:43:27,797 --> 00:43:29,199
She brought it for you.

979
00:43:29,265 --> 00:43:30,533
CRYING

980
00:43:30,600 --> 00:43:32,202
Do you want to get down?

981
00:43:32,268 --> 00:43:33,269
He's especially...

982
00:43:33,336 --> 00:43:36,439
- You don't want it?
- He's especially cranky today.

983
00:43:36,506 --> 00:43:38,808
- Whoosh.
- Airplane!

984
00:43:39,075 --> 00:43:40,777
THE PART-TIMER CAN'T HELP
BUT TURN INTO AN AIRPLANE

985
00:43:40,844 --> 00:43:42,011
Do you like your formula?

986
00:43:42,812 --> 00:43:44,247
Do you like it?

987
00:43:44,747 --> 00:43:46,683
SHE SNEAKILY APPROACHES THE COUCH

988
00:43:46,883 --> 00:43:47,951
DROPPING

989
00:43:48,017 --> 00:43:49,285
This darn formula.

990
00:43:50,553 --> 00:43:51,988
This darn formula.

991
00:43:53,923 --> 00:43:55,125
I want to cry, too.

992
00:43:55,191 --> 00:43:56,459
QUICKLY PICKS IT UP
BEFORE THE PART-TIMER CRIES

993
00:43:56,860 --> 00:43:58,561
LAUGHING AWKWARDLY

994
00:43:58,628 --> 00:43:59,863
I want to cry, too.

995
00:43:59,929 --> 00:44:00,930
GRINS

996
00:44:01,331 --> 00:44:03,800
- We need to wash it again.
- I'll cry before you do.

997
00:44:05,435 --> 00:44:07,837
